rdf:Description.lla:note: Fell while working on the boom brace. The ship was turned around, a rope thrown out, a seven foot bench thrown into the water and a boat put out. But he could not be rescued. Fuller description in the log book together with his effects. His effects included arithmetic and spelling books and a volume called "Moral Courage".

rdf:Description.lla:reason: Unfitness to proceed in the vessel

rdf:Description.lla:note: Appears to have served two spells on the ship. Recorded in the log as swearing and cursing in an argument about a piece of beef.
